				<td colspan="2"><span>Just for clarity:
<br />

<br />
The mez is and AoE 200' unresistable 20sec mez.   The imp casts it every 30sec.
<br />

<br />
DoTs break mez only when the damage per tick &gt; regen per tick.
<br />

<br />
So either every drops their regen buffs / gear and swallows a stinging wort potion, or  everyone focuses on fast cast spells and burst melee.
<br />

<br />
Also, the raid must know that Scarelings are  not to be killed until the zone in is clear.   The chanters keep them mezzed until the raid / group is set to take on the Ireblind imp.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
