				<td colspan="2"><span>I was in fear week before last and this guy was up at the normal west wall break point.  To answer someone's speculation above about him not using the mez unless multiple targets are around is not the case.  I was the only one in the zone and he did fire off his mez.  I think it was that the imp has a smaller agro radius than other fear denizens and he didn't mez until agro'ed.  
